He's a fraud, not a husband.

4
00:01:27,504 --> 00:01:29,714
Everything he said
when we were dating was a lie.

5
00:01:29,798 --> 00:01:31,049
He said his senior told him

6
00:01:31,132 --> 00:01:33,259
