144
00:14:19,483 --> 00:14:20,484
It's me.

145
00:14:23,028 --> 00:14:25,030
It's me, Gang-hwa. Cho Gang-hwa.

146
00:14:33,289 --> 00:14:34,290
Right.

147
00:14:35,291 --> 00:14:36,584
Cho Gang-hwa.

148
00:14:42,798 --> 00:14:46,051
